TileX.description: The x coordinate of the block the item frame is in

TileY.description: The y coordinate of the block the item frame is in

Warmup.description: The number of ticks until the fangs pop out of the ground

OwnerUUIDMost.description: The upper bits of the owner's UUID

OwnerUUIDLeast.description: The lower bits of the owner's UUID

Age.description: The number of ticks the item has been alive

PickupDelay.description: The number of ticks until a player can pick up this item

Owner.description:
The owner of the item  
 Only the owner can pick up the item

Thrower.description: The player who threw the item

M.description: The upper bits of the target player's UUID

L.description: The lower bits of the target player's UUID

Additive.description: Adds all of the modifiers' amounts to the current value of the attribute

Percentage.description:
For every modifier, multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the amount of the particular modifier.
 Functions the same as Operation 1 if there is only a single modifier with operation 1 or 2.
 However, for multiple modifiers it will multiply the modifiers rather than adding them

Multiplicative.description:
Multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the sum of the modifiers' amounts.

LeftOfUpsideDownDiagonal.description: Left of upside-down Diagonal (Per bend inverted)

RightOfDiagonal.description: Right of Diagonal (Per bend sinister inverted)
